name: DAO Bears
description: We are raising funds to buy the Chicago Bears from the McCaskey Family in order to restore the Monsters of the Midway to their previous glory. If we do purchase the Chicago Bears, every token holder will have a vote on every operational decision proportional to the amount they donate. Bear down!
payDisclosure: All proceeds will be refunded if we do not reach the required reserve to purchase the Chicago Bears Organization. Contributions are proportional to your delegation/voting power over the project.
